Watch More GTLive Here! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
USE: #GTLIVE and @matpatgt to send us comments & questions!

In honor of Thanksgiving tomorrow, we wanted to do something that'll put y'all in a good mood–so we're doing a Try Not to Laugh Challenge with videos SUBMITTED LIVE from You! We'll have Super Chat turned on for this stream, so you can make sure we watch your funny videos. Steph and I are pretty good at staying solemn, so we thought this would make the challenge more difficult. Send us the link to the video that you think will break us in the chat, and we'll throw it on!

NOTE: We will be checking videos in the background to be sure we don't show anything that isn't okay for most viewers. Please don't submit violent or overly risqué content.
